cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.MM

1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image segmentation from 3D electron microscopy.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses a deep structured learning method for segmentation.
3. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possibility as the paper deals with neuron segmentation.
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that could also apply to this paper due to the use of machine learning techniques.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but could apply as the paper deals with processing large volumes of 3D images.
